"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Adam White, the president of cryptocurrency firm Bakkt, is leaving the company he helped build from scratch as a founding executive.\\n\\nWhite spent the last three years at Bakkt, a company that launched in 2018 with the ambitious aim of making institutional crypto adoption a reality before pivoting to a suite of more[ retail-focused products](https://www.coindesk.com/business/2021/03/30/bakkt-digital-wallet-for-bitcoin-to-starbucks-points-goes-live-after-long-delay/).\\n\\nPrior to his time with Bakkt, White was VP and general manager for five years at cryptocurrency exchange Coinbase.\\n\\n‚ÄúAfter a great 3+ years at bakkt, next week will be my last,‚Äù [White said in a tweet on Thursday](https://twitter.com/whiteadaml/status/1474032915529015299?s=21). ‚ÄúI‚Äôve loved working at \\\\[the\\\\] intersection of crypto + markets and good to see the industry finding the balance between innovation & regulation. Lots of work still to do here but never been more optimistic about the future.‚Äù\\n\\nWhite did not reveal what opportunities he would be exploring next.\\n\\n> After a great 3+ years at bakkt, next week will be my last \\n  \\n I‚Äôve loved working at intersection of crypto + markets and good to see the industry finding the balance between innovation & regulation. Lots of work still to do here but never been more optimistic about the future üåï\\n>\\n> ‚Äî Adam White (@WhiteAdamL) [December 23, 2021](https://twitter.com/WhiteAdamL/status/1474032915529015299?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw)\\n\\nBakkt [went public](https://www.coindesk.com/business/2021/10/18/cryptocurrency-exchange-bakkt-falls-in-first-day-of-trading-after-spac-deal/) in October of this year following a merger with special purpose acquisition company VPC Impact Acquisition Holdings, and began trading on the New York Stock Exchange under the ticker symbol ‚ÄúBKKT.‚Äù\\n\\nShares in Bakkt [spiked around the end of October](https://www.coindesk.com/business/2021/10/25/bakkt-shares-surge-180-after-pacts-with-mastercard-fiserv-for-crypto-payments/) at above $40, but have since dropped sharply and were trading at $9.10 at the time of writing.\\n\\nAccording to an email sent to Bakkt staff this week that was seen by CoinDesk, White‚Äôs ‚Äúdeep expertise in crypto and a commitment to execution and innovation will be sorely missed.‚Äù\\n\\n‚ÄúWe‚Äôre fortunate to have a deep bench of leaders that are well positioned to help Bakkt achieve its vision of connecting the digital economy,‚Äù Bakkt CEO Gavin Michael wrote in the email.\\n\\nBakkt, which came charging out the gate with the weight of NYSE-owner Intercontinental Exchange behind it, has struggled to live up to the lofty expectations placed upon it during the crypto bear market in which it was born.\\n\\nThe company launched with Kelly Loeffler at the helm as CEO before she [left the firm in late-2019](https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2019/12/04/georgia-governor-appoints-bakkt-ceo-loeffler-as-new-us-senator/) to become a U.S. Senator from the state of Georgia. She [lost her reelection bid](https://www.coindesk.com/policy/2021/01/06/former-bakkt-ceo-kelly-loeffler-loses-senate-seat-democrats-retake-senate/) in the 2020 cycle.\",\"timestamp\":1640272561,\"title\":\"Bakkt President Adam White Announces His Departure\"},\"digest\":\"0kysYj5K_-jBgnACi0d2VgFk_7hn_57Jy7kw09Rkr78\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x52CEb287BEb81D61eDf413A8B3007b611E8917EA\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nQHBCPz2qtQmD3hGG3pD7NQfk4uG98r8LsuH3JMki2U\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"9ulaFHYEDsyrV15agdBQIBay7L_1kSeJhy4ULZBktmg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Dk3FrekxsmE06tguZ2U-YTnoZiTfuJxnD9wWlV1XxZaPrsqFGw6QxX7f7vOB4r6hdMqS7f-Fef1OWvH9rksvdg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xf8bca24910c14c75c0a522e4d8225f56f598a50cdb280a5e6fe4f1609a4e7a85794ed8f37bfb0ccc05332c67a7935abe384f063ec897dc916a9519babeb7e3df1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nQHBCPz2qtQmD3hGG3pD7NQfk4uG98r8LsuH3JMki2U\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"9ulaFHYEDsyrV15agdBQIBay7L_1kSeJhy4ULZBktmg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"0kysYj5K_-jBgnACi0d2VgFk_7hn_57Jy7kw09Rkr78\"}"